  <brief_title>A Clinical Study to Test Efficacy and Safety of CNTX-4975-05 in Patients With Osteoarthritis Knee Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Single Injection, 52-Week Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of an Intra-articular Injection of CNTX-4975-05 in Subjects With Chronic, Moderate-to-severe Osteoarthritis Knee Pain</official_title>
