  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a phase 3, randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled, single injection, 52-week
      study to evaluate the efficacy and safety of CNTX-4975-05 in subjects with chronic,
      moderate-to-severe osteoarthritis knee pain.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
